ic/weather/climate/gctb66ydw|title=Crosby 1981\u20132010 Averages|publisher=Met Office|accessdate=19 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n\n===Averages===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Period\n!Mean wind speed at 10m\n|-\n|Annual\n|{{Convert|11.8|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|January\n|{{Convert|13.5|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|February\n|{{Convert|13.3|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|March\n|{{Convert|12.7|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|April\n|{{Convert|11.1|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|May\n|{{Convert|10.6|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|June\n|{{Convert|11.1|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|July\n|{{Convert|11.7|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|August\n|{{Convert|8.6|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|September\n|{{Convert|11.5|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|October\n|{{Convert|12.0|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|November\n|{{Convert|12.6|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|-\n|December\n|{{Convert|12.4|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n|}\n{{col-3}}\n\n===Daily Extremes===\nHighest wind gusts reported in each month of the year.\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Period\n!Maximum Gusts \n!Date\n|-\n|January\n|{{Convert|88|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20110709125725/http://www.pol.ac.uk/appl/hist_met/windgust.pdf</ref>\n| 29 January 1938\n|-\n|February\n|{{Convert|83|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 26 February 1990\n|-\n|March\n|{{Convert|85|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 27 March 1966\n|-\n|April\n|{{Convert|73|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 23 April 1947\n|-\n|May\n|{{Convert|75|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 22 May 1966\n|-\n|June\n|{{Convert|62|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 5 June 1946\n|-\n|July\n|{{Convert|60|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 30 July 1946\n|-\n|August\n|{{Convert|67|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 20 August 1934 <br> 25 August 1957\n|-\n|September\n|{{Convert|72|kn|mph|abbr=on|order=flip}}\n| 20 September 198